model.spreadsheet

Class CourseDB

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.spreadsheet.CourseDB

  • public class CourseDB
extends java.lang.Object
    CourseDB generates unique courseID's for SpreadhseetCourses. The next ID to use are contained in a file called "courseDB.txt". Every time the ID is used it increments in the file. This class is a singleton.
    Author:
    jamesfazio
